      "review_summary": "The PR adds `console.warn` diagnostics to Discord component reply and exec approval interaction catch blocks while keeping the existing caught-error flow.\n\nPR surface: Source +10. Total +10 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main has empty catch blocks on Discord interaction reply, acknowledge, and follow-up paths, and the local REST wrapper can throw. I did not establish a live Discord failure reproduction in this read-only review.",
